WEBVTT

13:15.870 --> 13:17.870 line:80%
You are, with what you're doing now.

13:18.280 --> 13:20.920 line:80%
Is anyone else than you
giving away free offal?

13:21.120 --> 13:22.640 line:80%
Enough, Guo Dali.

13:22.800 --> 13:24.350 line:80%
Why bicker with a young girl?

13:24.350 --> 13:26.010 line:80%
She's only selling half a pig.
